{
  "stem": "19969.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 65.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But so life has its ups and down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Every family has tragedies and ours has had a great tragedy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We found that other families have experienced the same thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Cuba [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was called back as a [? strat ?] commander.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, I was a full colonel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was one-- assigned to the forces that were selected to make the invasion of Cuba, which as you know when Khrushchev backed down and agreed to take the missiles out of Cuba, that thing ended so I was only on for a year.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it did take a year out that I had not expected.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Strangely enough, the unit I was with at that time was not called for the Korean duty.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was with an infantry regiment, but it was not called.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Although other troops from the Colorado National Guard were called.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our air wing and medical battalion, tank battalion were all called to Korea.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went back to Germany about five-- five times since the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three of those trips included a visit to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I met with some survivors, German survivors, who were in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When arrived, they were political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I've gone through their museum there about three times since the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The present German government has maintained a small museum at Dachau and every time I have been there, I've been surprised at the great number of tourists who go through that grim facility on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, practically everything has been torn down now, but they have maintained two or three of those barracks, but they have been rebuilt.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
